Hes a good prof, study at least 3 hours per week and youll get an easy A+. Exams are all QCMs and if you follow his teachings and do the weekly practice Qcm, you will easily succeed.

After the first midterm, I had 50%, I finished his class with 70%. If you have him online, you should be fine because you can dewar him every lessons (recommended). avoid. I repeat: AVOID.
